Global_GetTeamPlayers.description:
Global
return {int,...} 
Returns a table of the Player IDs on the specified team

Global_GetUnitList.description:
Global
return {hUnit,...} 
Returns a list of units matching the specified unit type. Please keep in mind performance considerations when using GetUnitList. The itself is reasonably fast because it will build the lists on-demand and no more than once per frame,but the lists can be long and performing logic on all units (or even all creeps) can easily get pretty slow.

Global_PointToLineDistance.description:
Global
return {distance,closest_point,within} 
Returns a table containing the distance to the line segment,the closest point on the line segment,and whether the point is within the line segment (that is,the closest point is not one of the points).

Global_GetWorldBounds.description:
Global
return {float,float,float,float} 
Returns a table containing the min X,min Y,max X,and max Y bounds of the world.

Global_GetNeutralSpawners.description:
Global
return {{string,vector},...} 
Returns a table containing a list of camp-type and location pairs. Camp types are one of basic_N,ancient_N,basic_enemy_N,ancient_enemy_N,where N counts up from 0.

Global_GetDroppedItemList.description:
Global
return {{hItem,hOwner,nPlayer,vLocation},...} 
Returns a table of tables that list the item,owner,and location of items that have been dropped on the ground.

Global_GetAmountAlongLane.description:
Global
return {amount,distance} 
Returns the amount (0.0 - 1.0) along a lane,and distance from the lane of the specified location.

Global_GetHeroLastSeenInfo.description:
Global
return {{location,time_since_seen},...} 
Returns a table containing a list of locations and time_since_seen members,each representing the last seen location of a hero that player controls.

Global_GetLinearProjectiles.description:
Global
return {{location,caster,player,ability,velocity,radius,handle},...} 
Returns a table containing info about all visible linear projectiles.

Global_GetLinearProjectileByHandle.description:
Global
return {location,caster,player,ability,velocity,radius} 
Returns a table containing info about the specified linear projectile.

Global_GetAvoidanceZones.description:
Global
return {{location,ability,caster,radius},...} 
Returns a table containing info about all visible avoidance zones.

CDOTA_Bot_Script_GetNearbyHeroes.description:
CDOTA_Bot_Script:
return {hUnit,...} 
Returns a table of heroes,sorted closest-to-furthest,that are in the specified mode. If nMode is BOT_MODE_NONE,searches for all heroes. If bEnemies is true,nMode must be BOT_MODE_NONE. nRadius must be less than 1600.

